資料 並出現簡體字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2147175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2147175</a></span></span><br />\n記得有YUU嘅舖頭, 消費前都要諗一諗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而幸福醫藥又係TVB廣告贊助商, 仲報過狗搞狙擊團隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"small\"><br />\n幸福醫藥疑似報警，搞到個狙擊post無咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1816112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1816112</a></span></span><br />\n咩獅子山精神丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無綫電視立場偏頗仲擺咁多錢落去? 想買藥不如去藥房執<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"small\">大J: 「幸福醫藥」賣貴四倍價錢賺暴利，你仲買就係傻仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2205042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2205042</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n想要月曆不如買黃月曆. 想要貓貓月曆不如買阿瑪豆漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">懶人包<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n幸福止痛素（Paracetamol 500mg）係平野黎，大J藥房買平均$0.5一粒，7仔買就$2.X一粒；<br />\n幸福安泰敏（Loratadine 10mg）都係平野嚟，街邊賣緊5毫子左右，但幸福8片裝賣4-50蚊，呢個就係手足資訊<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LOnJM1CHo0I&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR1sFwIsWqkGrHUpTFyNv0oAww7VDnwooXYv0qyOU8ADGgPHgnvN7FHOSmo&amp;ab_channel=JASON\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLOnJM1CHo0I%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26fbclid%3DIwAR1sFwIsWqkGrHUpTFyNv0oAww7VDnwooXYv0qyOU8ADGgPHgnvN7FHOSmo%26ab_channel%3DJASON&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=080e9f41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LOnJM1CHo0I&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;fbclid=IwAR1sFwIsWqkGrHUpTFyNv0oAww7VDnwooXYv0qyOU8ADGgPHgnvN7FHOSmo&amp;ab_channel=JASON</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">心穎同A餐巴話佢地上年落咗三億廣告比TVB, 賺咁多唔怪得咁豪爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">【每日任務@ 16 Sep】<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幸福醫藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFortune.Pharmacal%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=d795ab36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Fortune.Pharmacal/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LYhdCPU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLYhdCPU.png&h=193a18b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n幸福醫藥賣得貴就唔係今日先講架喇，不過見仲有好多人買緊，就幫大家溫故知新吓，大J年初做過調查，發現一模一樣成份嘅藥，去藥房買平均只係5毫子一粒，但7-11係賣緊兩個幾一粒呀！<br />\n<br />\n點解賣咁貴？會唔會係因為啲錢落晒去TVB袋呀？舊團隊話你哋上年都落成3億廣告喎，咁咪即係賺香港人暴利，做出賣香港人嘅事？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">替代建議：有病要睇醫生，要買藥就買樂信或者去藥房</span></span><br />\n勿食藍色品牌：必理痛、幸福醫藥</strong><br />\n<br />\n留言template：<br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"gold\">無綫電視立場偏頗，新聞部扭曲事實、管理層打壓良心員工、編劇為執政者鷹犬洗刷污名，懇請 貴公司轉用其他宣傳渠道，例如蘋果日報、ViuTV、香港開電視等，以免間接資助一間為中共維穩的電視台。本人尊重 貴公司的市場推廣策略，但基於良心消費原則，本人只能無奈地暫停光顧，並呼籲朋友及家人抵制。</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"small\">Source：「幸福醫藥」賣貴四倍價錢賺暴利<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2FuLEWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FuLEWQ&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=e06ca891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2FuLEWQ</a></span></em><br />\n============================================<br />\n<blockquote><p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">【抵制 TVB戰線】</span></span></strong><br />\nFollow 抵制TVB戰線，每日派嬲，對方廣告費就億億聲咁跌！<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=696299c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb/</a>  </span></p><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><p class=\"center\"><strong>【TVB廣告商詳細名單】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/TVBAdData\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FTVBAdData&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=3d2b947d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/TVBAdData</a> </strong></p></span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後都要重申，<span class=\"red\">我地支持自由經濟，我地同意廣告商有賣廣告既自由，但顧客都有選擇買同唔買既自由</span>，我地只會抵制無良商戶，但唔會威脅佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"360e39df6c14db2b381c3fe72f1d60b77f8db528","tid":2269701,"uid":364068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4493897ed9ac46f5c360185401e52c567ad3a703","tid":2269701,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6uizoT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6uizoT.png&h=8c19bde8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dindong/posts/10159520135319276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdindong%2Fposts%2F10159520135319276&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=5f1766f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dindong/posts/10159520135319276</a></span><br />\n<br />\n萬寧母公司怡和譴責反送中運動, 係藍傢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PiovqnT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPiovqnT.jpg&h=ebc48d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqHoLnU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqHoLnU.png&h=bce28d65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"small\">點解身邊咁多人都入做咗Yuu會員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2260069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2260069</a><br />\n怡和旗下儲分app Yuu 整合惠康萬寧7.11 IKEA 索取大量個人資料 並出現簡體字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2147175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2147175</a></span></span><br />\n記得有YUU嘅舖頭, 消費前都要諗一諗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而幸福醫藥又係TVB廣告贊助商, 仲報過狗搞狙擊團隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"small\"><br />\n幸福醫藥疑似報警，搞到個狙擊post無咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1816112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1816112</a></span></span><br />\n咩獅子山精神丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無綫電視立場偏頗仲擺咁多錢落去? 想買藥不如去藥房執<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"small\">大J: 「幸福醫藥」賣貴四倍價錢賺暴利，你仲買就係傻仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2205042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2205042</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n想要月曆不如買黃月曆. 想要貓貓月曆不如買阿瑪豆漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打人馬座A*特登做咗示範<br />\n實測，代替幸福，去藥房買散裝藥<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1816453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1816453</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幸福我屌你老母咁撚串，我依家就教識全香港人買必理痛代替品，等你最好買嗰隻藥收皮<br />\n<br />\n利申：識人喺幸福做，隻必理痛真係幫佢賺咗好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）首先去搵緊間掛有白底紅十字的「Rx」標誌的藥房<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0yoJoT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0yoJoT.png&h=ca82e057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2）跟住行埋去同佢講想買散裝藥，俾個list佢唔使講藥名，我就俾咗下面個list佢，話每樣要10粒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hs8Dxi6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhs8Dxi6.png&h=b2d1bf6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）跟住佢同我講我比排裝我，好袋啲，之後俾咗三排藥我，總數收我$26<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZfkKsRT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZfkKsRT.png&h=4f1654b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5JQVzxa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5JQVzxa.png&h=0100b42f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幸福真係奸商，啲唔值錢嘅藥走去賣到幾蚊粒，仲要佢係同第二間廠買啲藥嘅有效成份返嚟，喺香港將啲有效成份撈埋其他嘢再Mark up幾倍賣比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 所以大家一定要抵制幸福</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d69416079a218d6ea793572c5fb91781c3b65629","tid":2269701,"uid":364068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"希望癲噹巴第時會考慮同其他良心品牌合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Anj8Hg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Anj8Hg.jpg&h=ad886df4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da0b8ab79a94ef2b3857a4014bd692c43fc8338b","tid":2269701,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e958553197d1a7d6b1b9e42471876192a6d56e34","tid":2269701,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca24cf5c5d2b98133386b76e04f89ccc3881b88f","tid":2269701,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces